  "taskId": "task_1778171272476_457",
  "requestedModel": "anti-claude-sonnet-4.6-thinking",
  "text": "요청하신 백엔드 캠페인 CRUD API 개발을 완료했습니다.\n핵심 요구사항인 소유권자(`advertiser_id`) 확인 로직을 포함하여 구현했습니다.\n\n### 1. 데이터베이스 스키마 (`schema.prisma`)\n캠페인, 광고 소재, 광고주 모델을 정의했습니다. 캠페인은 `advertiserId`를 통해 광고주와 명확한 소유 관계를 가집니다.\n\n```prisma\n// OUTPUT/prisma/schema.prisma\n\ngenerator client {\n  provider = \"prisma-client-js\"\n}\n\ndatasource db {\n  provider = \"postgresql\"\n  url      = env(\"DATABASE_URL\")\n}\n\nmodel Advertiser {\n  id        String     @id @default(cuid())\n  email     String     @unique\n  password  String\n  name      String?\n  createdAt DateTime   @default(now())\n  updatedAt DateTime   @updatedAt\n  campaigns Campaign[]\n}\n\nmodel Campaign {\n  id            String       @id @default(cuid())\n  name          String\n  status        CampaignStatus @default(INACTIVE)\n  startDate     DateTime\n  endDate       DateTime?\n  budget        Float\n  createdAt     DateTime     @default(now())\n  updatedAt     DateTime     @updatedAt\n  advertiser    Advertiser   @relation(fields: [advertiserId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)\n  advertiserId  String\n  adCreatives   AdCreative[]\n}\n\nmodel AdCreative {\n  id          String   @id @default(cuid())\n  title       String\n  description String\n  imageUrl    String\n  targetUrl   String\n  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())\n  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt\n  campaign    Campaign @relation(fields: [campaignId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)\n  campaignId  String\n}\n\nenum CampaignStatus {\n  ACTIVE\n  PAUSED\n  INACTIVE\n  COMPLETED\n}\n```\n\n### 2. 캠페인 API 구현 (`campaigns` 모듈)\n인증된 사용자(`Advertiser`)를 식별하기 위한 `@GetUser()` 데코레이터와 `JwtAuthGuard`를 적용했습니다. 서비스 로직의 모든 메서드는 `advertiserId`를 기준으로 데이터를 필터링하여, 자신의 캠페인에만 접근하고 수정할 수 있도록 보장합니다.\n\n#### **DTO (Data Transfer Object)**\n`class-validator`를 사용하여 API 요청 시 데이터 유효성을 검사합니다.\n\n```typescript\n// OUTPUT/src/campaigns/dto/create-campaign.dto.ts\n\nimport { IsString, IsNotEmpty, IsDate, IsOptional, IsNumber, IsIn } from 'class-validator';\nimport { Type } from 'class-transformer';\n\nconst campaignStatuses = ['ACTIVE', 'PAUSED', 'INACTIVE', 'COMPLETED'] as const;\ntype CampaignStatus = typeof campaignStatuses[number];\n\n\nexport class CreateCampaignDto {\n  @IsString()\n  @IsNotEmpty()\n  name: string;\n\n  @IsOptional()\n  @IsIn(campaignStatuses)\n  status?: CampaignStatus;\n\n  @IsDate()\n  @Type(() => Date)\n  @IsNotEmpty()\n  startDate: Date;\n\n  @IsDate()\n  @Type(() => Date)\n  @IsOptional()\n  endDate?: Date;\n\n  @IsNumber()\n  @IsNotEmpty()\n  budget: number;\n}\n```\n\n```typescript\n// OUTPUT/src/campaigns/dto/update-campaign.dto.ts\n\nimport { PartialType } from '@nestjs/mapped-types';\nimport { CreateCampaignDto } from './create-campaign.dto';\n\nexport class UpdateCampaignDto extends PartialType(CreateCampaignDto) {}\n```\n\n#### **캠페인 컨트롤러 (`campaigns.controller.ts`)**\nAPI 엔드포인트를 정의하고, JWT 인증 가드를 통해 모든 요청을 보호합니다.\n\n```typescript\n// OUTPUT/src/campaigns/campaigns.controller.ts\n\nimport { Controller, Get, Post, Body, Patch, Param, Delete, UseGuards, NotFoundException } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { CampaignsService } from './campaigns.service';\nimport { CreateCampaignDto } from './dto/create-campaign.dto';\nimport { UpdateCampaignDto } from './dto/update-campaign.dto';\nimport { JwtAuthGuard } from '../auth/jwt-auth.guard';\nimport { GetUser } from '../auth/get-user.decorator';\nimport { Advertiser } from '@prisma/client';\n\n@UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard)\n@Controller('campaigns')\nexport class CampaignsController {\n  constructor(private readonly campaignsService: CampaignsService) {}\n\n  @Post()\n  create(@Body() createCampaignDto: CreateCampaignDto, @GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\n    return this.campaignsService.create(createCampaignDto, user.id);\n  }\n\n  @Get()\n  findAll(@GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\n    return this.campaignsService.findAll(user.id);\n  }\n\n  @Get(':id')\n  async findOne(@Param('id') id: string, @GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\n    const campaign = await this.campaignsService.findOne(id, user.id);\n    if (!campaign) {\n      throw new NotFoundException(`Campaign with ID \"${id}\" not found`);\n    }\n    return campaign;\n  }\n\n  @Patch(':id')\n  update(@Param('id') id: string, @Body() updateCampaignDto: UpdateCampaignDto, @GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\n    return this.campaignsService.update(id, updateCampaignDto, user.id);\n  }\n\n  @Delete(':id')\n  remove(@Param('id') id: string, @GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\n    return this.campaignsService.remove(id, user.id);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### **캠페인 서비스 (`campaigns.service.ts`)**\n핵심 비즈니스 로직입니다. Prisma 클라이언트를 사용하여 데이터베이스와 상호작용하며, 모든 쿼리(`where` 절)에 `advertiserId`를 포함시켜 데이터 소유권을 강제합니다.\n\n```typescript\n// OUTPUT/src/campaigns/campaigns.service.ts\n\nimport { Injectable, NotFoundException, ForbiddenException } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { PrismaService } from '../prisma/prisma.service';\nimport { CreateCampaignDto } from './dto/create-campaign.dto';\nimport { UpdateCampaignDto } from './dto/update-campaign.dto';\nimport { Campaign } from '@prisma/client';\n\n@Injectable()\nexport class CampaignsService {\n  constructor(private prisma: PrismaService) {}\n\n  async create(createCampaignDto: CreateCampaignDto, advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign> {\n    return this.prisma.campaign.create({\n      data: {\n        ...createCampaignDto,\n        advertiserId,\n      },\n    });\n  }\n\n  async findAll(advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign[]> {\n    return this.prisma.campaign.findMany({\n      where: { advertiserId },\n    });\n  }\n\n  async findOne(id: string, advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign | null> {\n    return this.prisma.campaign.findFirst({\n      where: { id, advertiserId },\n    });\n  }\n\n  async update(id: string, updateCampaignDto: UpdateCampaignDto, advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign> {\n    const campaign = await this.findOne(id, advertiserId);\n    if (!campaign) {\n      throw new NotFoundException(`Campaign with ID \"${id}\" not found`);\n    }\n\n    return this.prisma.campaign.update({\n      where: { id },\n      data: updateCampaignDto,\n    });\n  }\n\n  async remove(id: string, advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign> {\n    const campaign = await this.findOne(id, advertiserId);\n    if (!campaign) {\n      throw new NotFoundException(`Campaign with ID \"${id}\" not found`);\n    }\n\n    return this.prisma.campaign.delete({\n      where: { id },\n    });\n  }\n}\n```\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"prisma/schema.prisma\",\n    \"content\": \"generator client {\\n  provider = \\\"prisma-client-js\\\"\\n}\\n\\ndatasource db {\\n  provider = \\\"postgresql\\\"\\n  url      = env(\\\"DATABASE_URL\\\")\\n}\\n\\nmodel Advertiser {\\n  id        String     @id @default(cuid())\\n  email     String     @unique\\n  password  String\\n  name      String?\\n  createdAt DateTime   @default(now())\\n  updatedAt DateTime   @updatedAt\\n  campaigns Campaign[]\\n}\\n\\nmodel Campaign {\\n  id            String       @id @default(cuid())\\n  name          String\\n  status        CampaignStatus @default(INACTIVE)\\n  startDate     DateTime\\n  endDate       DateTime?\\n  budget        Float\\n  createdAt     DateTime     @default(now())\\n  updatedAt     DateTime     @updatedAt\\n  advertiser    Advertiser   @relation(fields: [advertiserId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)\\n  advertiserId  String\\n  adCreatives   AdCreative[]\\n}\\n\\nmodel AdCreative {\\n  id          String   @id @default(cuid())\\n  title       String\\n  description String\\n  imageUrl    String\\n  targetUrl   String\\n  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())\\n  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt\\n  campaign    Campaign @relation(fields: [campaignId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)\\n  campaignId  String\\n}\\n\\nenum CampaignStatus {\\n  ACTIVE\\n  PAUSED\\n  INACTIVE\\n  COMPLETED\\n}\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/campaigns/dto/create-campaign.dto.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { IsString, IsNotEmpty, IsDate, IsOptional, IsNumber, IsIn } from 'class-validator';\\nimport { Type } from 'class-transformer';\\n\\nconst campaignStatuses = ['ACTIVE', 'PAUSED', 'INACTIVE', 'COMPLETED'] as const;\\ntype CampaignStatus = typeof campaignStatuses[number];\\n\\n\\nexport class CreateCampaignDto {\\n  @IsString()\\n  @IsNotEmpty()\\n  name: string;\\n\\n  @IsOptional()\\n  @IsIn(campaignStatuses)\\n  status?: CampaignStatus;\\n\\n  @IsDate()\\n  @Type(() => Date)\\n  @IsNotEmpty()\\n  startDate: Date;\\n\\n  @IsDate()\\n  @Type(() => Date)\\n  @IsOptional()\\n  endDate?: Date;\\n\\n  @IsNumber()\\n  @IsNotEmpty()\\n  budget: number;\\n}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/campaigns/dto/update-campaign.dto.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { PartialType } from '@nestjs/mapped-types';\\nimport { CreateCampaignDto } from './create-campaign.dto';\\n\\nexport class UpdateCampaignDto extends PartialType(CreateCampaignDto) {}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/campaigns/campaigns.controller.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Controller, Get, Post, Body, Patch, Param, Delete, UseGuards, NotFoundException } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { CampaignsService } from './campaigns.service';\\nimport { CreateCampaignDto } from './dto/create-campaign.dto';\\nimport { UpdateCampaignDto } from './dto/update-campaign.dto';\\nimport { JwtAuthGuard } from '../auth/jwt-auth.guard';\\nimport { GetUser } from '../auth/get-user.decorator';\\nimport { Advertiser } from '@prisma/client';\\n\\n@UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard)\\n@Controller('campaigns')\\nexport class CampaignsController {\\n  constructor(private readonly campaignsService: CampaignsService) {}\\n\\n  @Post()\\n  create(@Body() createCampaignDto: CreateCampaignDto, @GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\\n    return this.campaignsService.create(createCampaignDto, user.id);\\n  }\\n\\n  @Get()\\n  findAll(@GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\\n    return this.campaignsService.findAll(user.id);\\n  }\\n\\n  @Get(':id')\\n  async findOne(@Param('id') id: string, @GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\\n    const campaign = await this.campaignsService.findOne(id, user.id);\\n    if (!campaign) {\\n      throw new NotFoundException(`Campaign with ID \\\"${id}\\\" not found`);\\n    }\\n    return campaign;\\n  }\\n\\n  @Patch(':id')\\n  update(@Param('id') id: string, @Body() updateCampaignDto: UpdateCampaignDto, @GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\\n    return this.campaignsService.update(id, updateCampaignDto, user.id);\\n  }\\n\\n  @Delete(':id')\\n  remove(@Param('id') id: string, @GetUser() user: Advertiser) {\\n    return this.campaignsService.remove(id, user.id);\\n  }\\n}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"src/campaigns/campaigns.service.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Injectable, NotFoundException, ForbiddenException } from '@nestjs/common';\\nimport { PrismaService } from '../prisma/prisma.service';\\nimport { CreateCampaignDto } from './dto/create-campaign.dto';\\nimport { UpdateCampaignDto } from './dto/update-campaign.dto';\\nimport { Campaign } from '@prisma/client';\\n\\n@Injectable()\\nexport class CampaignsService {\\n  constructor(private prisma: PrismaService) {}\\n\\n  async create(createCampaignDto: CreateCampaignDto, advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign> {\\n    return this.prisma.campaign.create({\\n      data: {\\n        ...createCampaignDto,\\n        advertiserId,\\n      },\\n    });\\n  }\\n\\n  async findAll(advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign[]> {\\n    return this.prisma.campaign.findMany({\\n      where: { advertiserId },\\n    });\\n  }\\n\\n  async findOne(id: string, advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign | null> {\\n    return this.prisma.campaign.findFirst({\\n      where: { id, advertiserId },\\n    });\\n  }\\n\\n  async update(id: string, updateCampaignDto: UpdateCampaignDto, advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign> {\\n    const campaign = await this.findOne(id, advertiserId);\\n    if (!campaign) {\\n      throw new NotFoundException(`Campaign with ID \\\"${id}\\\" not found`);\\n    }\\n\\n    return this.prisma.campaign.update({\\n      where: { id },\\n      data: updateCampaignDto,\\n    });\\n  }\\n\\n  async remove(id: string, advertiserId: string): Promise<Campaign> {\\n    const campaign = await this.findOne(id, advertiserId);\\n    if (!campaign) {\\n      throw new NotFoundException(`Campaign with ID \\\"${id}\\\" not found`);\\n    }\\n\\n    return this.prisma.campaign.delete({\\n      where: { id },\\n    });\\n  }\\n}\\n\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n<review_request>\n{\n  \"title\": \"[리뷰] 백엔드 캠페인 CRUD API 구현\",\n  \"assignee\": \"dev_advisor\",\n  \"message\": \"캠페인 CRUD API 개발을 완료했습니다. NestJS와 Prisma를 사용하여 구현했으며, JWT 인증을 통해 얻은 `advertiserId`를 기준으로 모든 API 요청에 대한 소유권자 확인 로직을 포함했습니다. 데이터베이스 스키마, DTO, 컨트롤러, 서비스 코드 리뷰 부탁드립니다.\"\n}\n</review_request>",
